description: The closer the Clock is set to midnight, the closer scientists believe the world is to global disaster.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Doomsday Clock how many minutes till midnight
Alexa, ask Doomsday Clock what the time is
Alexa, ask Doomsday Clock when is midnight
name: Doomsday Clock
shortDescription: This skill lets you know the status of the doomsday clock.
